    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"spell-description\">\n  <p>\n    <strong>School</strong>&nbsp;necromancy&nbsp;[acid, death];\n    <strong>Level</strong>&nbsp;antipaladin 4, cleric/oracle 4, sorcerer/wizard 4;\n    \n    \n    \n    \n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Casting Time</strong>&nbsp;1 standard action<br>\n    <strong>Components</strong>&nbsp;V, S<br>\n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Range</strong>&nbsp;touch<br>\n    \n    <strong>Targets</strong>&nbsp;living creature touched<br>\n    \n    <strong>Duration</strong>&nbsp;instantaneous and 1 minute/level (see text)<br>\n    <strong>Saving Throw</strong>&nbsp;Fortitude negates or Reflex half (see text);&nbsp;<strong>Spell Resistance</strong>&nbsp;yes<br>\n  </p>\n  <h2>Description</h2>\n  <p>The target creature dies if it fails a Fortitude saving throw and its Hit Dice are no more than half your caster level.</p><p>If it dies, its corpse rapidly putrefies. The next creature to touch the corpse within 1 minute per level of the target's death causes the corpse to explode in a 10-foot-radius burst, dealing 3d6 points of acid damage (Reflex half).</p>\n</div>\n",
